In terms of application segmentation, the nail gun market caters to a wide range of industries such as construction, manufacturing, and woodworking. Industrial construction requires heavy-duty nail guns capable of handling large volumes of work efficiently, while residential construction may demand more lightweight and versatile options for quick and precise installations. Furniture manufacturing relies on precision nail guns that can work with different materials and nail sizes, emphasizing the need for specialized products tailored to specific applications.

